    to the hand, by returning this Tamer to the hand, you may play 1 13000 DP or
    lower red Digimon card with [Avian]/[Bird]/[Beast]/[Animal]/[Sovereign]\_in one
    of its traits (other than [Sea Animal]) from your hand without paying the cost.
    For each of your opponent's security cards, remove 2000 from this effect's playable
